<h2 id="FAQ–Frequently-asked-question-about-Fashion-and-Lifestyle">6-&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://indieseducation.com/introduction-to-fashion-and-lifestyle/#FAQ%E2%80%93Frequently-asked-question-about-Fashion-and-Lifestyle">FAQ’s – Frequently asked question about Fashion and Lifestyle –</a></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>1.&nbsp;Difference between fashion and lifestyle.</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Fashion and lifestyle are the main essences of a person’s personality.<br>Fashion is what an individual carries no matter what it is like –<br>1- Cloths<br>2 – accessories,<br>3 – watches,<br>4 – shoes,<br>5 – Jackets<br>6 – Winter or summer collection etc.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>2.&nbsp;What is fashion all about?</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Fashion is all about following what’s being in trending and evolving according to it. Fashion keeps on repeating it from generation to generation. People have different tastes and perceptions about fashion but for a simple person “Fashion is what makes you feel comfortable”.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>3.&nbsp;How fashions influence us on everyday life?</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Fashion influence too much especially on young lads of society. Fashion has become a way of living and a way of showcasing yourself in society to get respect from others.<br>If one doesn’t have a good fashion sense or even says a basic fashion sense then people I the society will start to push them away from the people who are well presented.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>4.&nbsp;Impact of fashion on youth and their lifestyle –</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Fashion and Lifestyle has a huge impact on youth. Youth try to experiment more and more on themselves to get to know about their own taste of fashion.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>5.&nbsp;What are Positive &amp; negative effects of fashion on society –</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>There are many effects of fashion and lifestyle, if fashion is followed wrongly or wore something inappropriate then it’s not worth it and if lifestyle Is bad then there is not worthy of getting a good life.</p>
